text: Gabriela Dabrowski and Mariana Duque were the defending champions, but both players are participating at the 2015 Pan American Games. Eva Hrdinová and Shahar Pe'er won the tournament, defeating Alona Fomina and Sofiya Kovalets in the final, 6–1, 6–3. == Seeds == == Draw == == References == * Draw Reinert Open - Doubles
